text: José Curiel (22 March 1937 – 8 January 2022) was a Venezuelan politician. He was a member of Copei. He was Governor of Falcón from 1996 to 2000. He was born in Coro, Venezuela. Curiel died at a hospital in Caracas, Venezuela on 8 January 2022 from lung cancer, at the age of 84. ==References== Category:1937 births Category:2022 deaths Category:Deaths from lung cancer Category:Venezuelan politicians
